Building out-of-sourcedir on Linux
----------------------------------

set JAVA_HOME, e.g. :

export JAVA_HOME="$(readlink -e $(which java) | sed s/\\/jre\\/bin\\/java//)"

32bit:

mkdir build ; cd build ; qmake ../launcher.pro ; make ; cd ..

64 bit (qmake seems to need some proding):

mkdir build ; cd build ; qmake -spec linux-g++-64 ../launcher.pro ; make ; cd ..